title: Plan Bay Area EIR: Additional Trend Growth Boundaries
name: Plan Bay Area EIR: Additional Trend Growth Boundaries
description:
Metropolitan Transportation Commission

For the Plan Bay Area EIR planning effort, two growth boundary options are being considered.  If you combine the areas in this data set with the areas in the strict data set (/overlays/261910), the result is the "trend" growth boundaries, which are intended to represent a continuation in the trend of growth boundary expansion.

David Ory (dory@mtc.ca.gov)
